==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Waistband
<hw>Waist"band</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
band which encompasses the waist; esp., one on the upper part of
breeches, trousers, pantaloons, skirts, or the like.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A sash worn by women around the waist.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Waistcloth</ent>⟦br⟧
